@startuml
left to right direction
actor "企业用户" as User

rectangle "系统" {
    usecase "信息修改" as InfoModify
    usecase "密码重置" as PasswordReset
}

User --> InfoModify : 修改企业名称、手机号等基本信息
InfoModify --> System : 验证新信息
System --> InfoModify : 更新信息

User --> PasswordReset : 按照系统提示步骤操作
PasswordReset --> System : 验证身份
System --> PasswordReset : 修改密码
@enduml